dct_title_s: Beograd : Plan grad - city map / map design & publishing Gizi Map. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Title from panel. At head of panel title: Magic Map. Includes text, ancillary suburb map, ancillary "Parking zone" city-center map, specimen map, coverage map, color illustrations, and publisher's advertisement. Street index, directory to points of interest/municipal services, 1:420,000-scale road map of "Okolina Beograda", and 6 numbered suburb maps on verso.
